Introduction

fromis_9 is a five-member girl group. They were formed through the reality show Idol School. Originally as nine, they officially debuted on January 24, 2018, with the mini album To. Heart. The group, in addition to making its debut showcase on January 25, also made its television debut on the MCountdown music program.

Their group name stands as a promise to their viewers to be the best girl group and their official motto is: "Promise now, cherish it preciously~ We will grow as into your idols. Hello, we are fromis_9!"

Flover (Fandom Name) Explanation: Combination of "fromis_9" and "clover". It refers to the fact that fromis_9 and the fans have a promise to share happy moments together.

On August 16, 2021, Pledis Entertainment announced that fromis_9 would be leaving Off The Record and would now be managed by Pledis Entertainment. In July 2022, it was revealed that the members' existing contracts from Off The Record have expired. Following this, all of them signed new exclusive contracts with Pledis Entertainment, except for Jang Gyuri.

On November 29, 2024, Pledis Entertainment announced that all eight members would not renew their contracts following their contract expiration on December 31, 2024.

On January 26, 2025, it was announced that members Hayoung, Jiwon, Chaeyoung, Nagyung, and Jiheon had signed an exclusive contract with ASND while members Saerom, Jisun, and Seoyeon officially parted ways with the group.
